<br>
As for Durability though, I still haven't seen conclusive evidence one way or the other. The in-game description appears to be somewhat different than what is stated in the txt file. If Durability applies only to the base, then the in-game description seems out of place. If, however, it does include gear and any stamina bonuses they might add, then I think the skill itself is mislabeled and causes confusion. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukayleighdrake.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KayleighDrake</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/02 1:47:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12946.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Archetype Abilities question</span><hr size=1> Let me get this straight.<br>
